# Git Workflow Rules for Treasury Hugo Site

## Default Branch

**The default branch is `master`, NOT `main`.**

When creating pull requests, always target `master`:

```bash
# Correct
gh pr create --base master --head your-feature-branch

# WRONG - will fail
gh pr create --base main --head your-feature-branch
```

## Branch Naming

Feature branches should follow the pattern:
- `feature/description` - New features
- `fix/description` - Bug fixes
- `content/description` - Content updates

## Creating PRs

Always verify the base branch before creating a PR:
```bash
# Check available branches
gh api repos/{owner}/{repo}/branches --jq '.[].name'

# Create PR against master
gh pr create --base master --title "Title" --body "Description"
```
